            <p className="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style={{ color: "#081C2E" }}>• Identify hazards — falls, falling objects, unstable surfaces, wind, heat stress in the KSA desert environment, dust storms, electrical hazards, proximity to moving machinery.</p>

